{"ja240:0.1":"Jataka ","ja240:0.2":"Dukanipata ","ja240:0.3":"Upahanavagga ","ja240:0.4":"10. Mahapingalajataka ","ja240:1.1":"“Sabbo jano himsito pingalena, ","ja240:1.2":"Tasmim mate paccaya vedayanti; ","ja240:1.3":"Piyo nu te asi akanhanetto, ","ja240:1.4":"Kasma nu tvam rodasi dvarapala”. ","ja240:2.1":"“Na me piyo asi akanhanetto, ","ja240:2.2":"Bhayami paccagamanaya tassa; ","ja240:2.3":"Ito gato himseyya maccurajam, ","ja240:2.4":"So himsito aneyya puna idha”. ","ja240:3.1":"“Daddho vahasahassehi, ","ja240:3.2":"sitto ghatasatehi so; ","ja240:3.3":"Parikkhata ca sa bhumi, ","ja240:3.4":"ma bhayi nagamissati”ti. ","ja240:4.1":"Mahapingalajatakam dasamam. ","ja240:4.2":"Upahanavaggo navamo. ","ja240:5.1":"Tassuddanam ","ja240:6.1":"Varupahana khujja vikannakako, ","ja240:6.2":"Asitabhuya pancamavacchanakho; ","ja240:6.3":"Dija pemavaruttamaekapadam, ","ja240:6.4":"Kuminamukha pingalakena dasati. "}